b"We have decided to stop advertising on Facebook and Instagram through the end of this year\xe2\x80\x93 or, until meaningful steps are taken to address the proliferation of hate speech and false information. 

Our brand's core values require that Facebook, Inc. create an environment that allows for real conversation while remaining safe and welcoming\xe2\x80\x93 now and for the long term.

We're so grateful for this community and the connections we make here. It's a platform where we can take a stand for equality, justice and peace, and work together towards a healthier, happier future where everyone can thrive. That's why we want to make sure it's a safe and inclusive space for all. 

We hope to be back soon. Until then, you can connect with us on Clorox.com and find us on Twitter (@Clorox), Pinterest (@Clorox), and YouTube (@Clorox) to stay in the loop on new products, deals, and community news. We'll see you there soon!"
